        {
            "id": 6008540,
            "title": "群光5月營收月增1% 兩產品表現亮眼",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電腦週邊廠群光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2385:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2385-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告營收 81.2 億元，月增 1%；累計前 5 月營收 394.29 億元，年成長 1%；群光指出，雖然關稅使得品牌客戶較為謹慎，不過相機模組、監控攝影仍表現亮眼。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008540%2Fl%2F1305338731fbc4331245fa6f1334142a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">群光5月營收81.2億元月增1% 面臨關稅仍有產品表現亮眼。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群光表示，今年受到川普關稅政策影響，品牌客戶皆謹慎以對，雖然目前為關稅暫緩課徵 90 天期內，市場需求仍較為保守。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群光提到，由於消費者期待筆電擁有高品質的影像表現，因此筆電相機模組受惠於規格升級，價格穩定向上；針對商用市場的監控攝影機亦較不受市場不確定性的干擾，今年以來需求暢旺，來自歐美客戶訂單十分踴躍。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群光指出，由於 RTX50 系列 GPU 出貨漸趨順暢，有利於群光集團擴大第 2 季的大瓦特數電競筆電電源出貨，推升營收成長。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群光表示，會因應客戶要求擴大泰國產能規模，目前群光集團已有三座泰國廠，其中兩座新廠正在加速量產中，預計今年整體泰國廠營收貢獻可達 25~30%，主要供應美國市場。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
